Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you enjoying your time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.50,0:00:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.87,0:00:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, how do you\Nusually spend your days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine\Nthat chores take up all of your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.81,0:00:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the magazines Ms. Yurie lends me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and do some sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You know, I'm thinking of going out\Nthe next time I have a day off of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, if you're going to be gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,would you still like me\Nto make lunch and dinner for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You would also go with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've realized\Nyou might want to go to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.96,0:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Uh, no...\N- Would you rather not go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.75,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.37,0:00:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't, uh... I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no reason to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be a nuisance\Nif I was there alongside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You are not a nuisance\Nand you don't need a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.18,0:01:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, but I'll... I'll be in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.67,0:01:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I am certain you wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wear that kimono\Nfrom the day you arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, do you have any other concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.32,0:01:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. It's settled then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so confused.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.97,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He hadn't said it directly,\Nand it never would've crossed my mind.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.72,0:01:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finalized with little fanfare,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}our first date was set.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,MY HAPPY MARRIAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,EPISODE 3\NTHE FIRST DATE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo, may I come in, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.96,0:03:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.18,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And how are the preparations going?\NNeed anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.39,0:03:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We had this mirror put in here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This looks so out of place on me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miss Miyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have your makeup done?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really used makeup before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you would allow me\Nto help you with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I am not prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what we can do. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have all the tools\Nand makeup that you could want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.17,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,None of it is anything too fancy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I have no doubt
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that once applied,\Nthey will look very nice on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I'll be starting\Nwith face powder,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,so gently close your eyes if you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. We're all done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have truly bloomed\Nlike a flower, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what the Young Master will say\Nwhen he sees you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you'll be done soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm on my way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.70,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just... I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.64,0:05:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, may I ask\Nwhere we're going today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes. I didn't tell you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.43,0:06:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll stop by my workplace first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not anything\Nto concern yourself with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Parking is difficult,\Nso I'll leave the car there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the place\Nwhere Lord Kudo works.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, hey, there!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That really you Commander?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a tick,\Naren't you supposed to be off duty today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am. I'm only here to park the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.83,0:07:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! And who do we have over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.57,0:07:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's escorting me today. Stop prying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! A guest\Nof the Commander is a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And my, my! She is just beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.09,0:07:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I told you to stop prying\Nand you chose not to listen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsie daisy! My apologies, heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop dawdling at the gate chatting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go return to your post.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! Please excuse me, Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.70,0:07:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What a menace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.83,0:07:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Godo is an aide\Nwho works alongside me relatively often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quite gifted\Nwith the supernatural skill set
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,though I don't like admitting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, is there any place\Nthat you'd like to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.26,0:07:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything you want to buy\Nor are in need of?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do I do?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't think of\Na single thing that I want.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to join me\Nfor some shopping errands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.66,0:08:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the host and I was distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to say sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy this to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.93,0:08:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be scolded\Nby anyone, including me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no need to think\Nthat you'll ever be a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never think that of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who wanted you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, don't get lost looking around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.36,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How can anyone\Npossibly say that he's cruel...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when he's so kind?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you send Miyo off to Kudo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.05,0:09:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My eldest should've gotten her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, well, that was the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Until I received the matrimonial proposal\Nfrom the Kudos.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}How could I turn down that offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo's mother was an Usuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A fact you are very well aware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, she didn't\Ninherit the Usuba gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, there's a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyo's child will inherit it\Nthrough the bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.63,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really so desperate\Nfor Usuba's abilities, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Usubas' supernatural abilities\Nfar exceed all of our own gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Families such as ours cannot afford\Nfor the Kudos
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}to become even more powerful\Nthan they already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kudo will lose interest in Miyo\Nwhen he realizes
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that she doesn't have any sort of ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It will happen, and when it does,\Nyou are more than welcome to take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whenever you whisk her off the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.31,0:10:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll be beside herself with joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know you favor your youngest,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but for you to go out of your way\Nto throw out Miyo?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's absurd to discard a goose\Nthat could lay a golden egg.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.63,0:10:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. So it's safe for me to assume
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that the Saimoris will stay out\Nof whatever happens to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've all but abandoned her anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.54,0:10:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no interest\Nin where she is or how she's surviving,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,whether she's alive or if she's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, then, if that's how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tatsuishis will have\NMiyo Saimori no matter the cost.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't let the Kudos steal her away.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tell me what my father\Nand Mr. Tatsuishi are talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know\Nall of the specifics, Miss Kaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it seems to be about Miss Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why would they waste\Na single breath on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I have no idea, Miss. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaya, there's really no need\Nto raise your voice like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Koji, are you trying to lecture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would my sister ever come up again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fathers don't have\Nany reason to talk about her, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we can go shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The weather's so nice out today,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so we may as well enjoy ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, remember\Nthat new department store just opened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we could take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.94,0:11:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay, we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.36,0:11:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's not like\NI have anything else going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A brand new store opened up\Non the middle road.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Its interior...\N-{\i1}What a fake smile!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure he still thinks about my sister.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's at the Kudos' home,\Nprobably nearly dead by now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everything is so annoying!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,SUZUSHIMAYA KIMONO SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This shop is Suzushimaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kudos have been patrons here\Nsince the old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Every now and again,\Nthey tailor clothes for the Emperor too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm! It's quite a prestigious place, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to see you, Mr. Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already selected a few items for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I should hope\Nthat they will suit the requests
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.16,0:12:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,we had received from you in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're in the back room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, Mr. Kudo,\Nthe time has finally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, that's not what this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no need to act coy\Nabout what's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If I'm not mistaken,\Nthis is the first time
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that you've brought\Na young lady here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.77,0:13:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well, she isn't wrong...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Young Master, were you aware?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw Miss Miyo sewing her own clothes\Nsince they're so worn out.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.15,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was about to say something to her,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it seemed like\Nshe didn't want us to know about it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such ragged clothes would\Nmake sense for a peasant farmer,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.91,0:13:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but not a Saimori.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's more, she only has\None good kimono to wear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she were properly cared for,\Nshe would own far more.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That prestigious family\Nshould've seen to it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}- Mr. Kudo.\N- Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right, Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think\Nwill look the best on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,In my opinion, lighter colors would likely\Nsuit her hair and complexion the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This one, and maybe this combination...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.27,0:13:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... And that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.08,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A very fine piece that would\Nalso suit the young Miss well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I should tell you\Nthat it will take some time to tailor,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so it may be a little out of season\Nby the time it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It would be perfect for her.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.34,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, one of that material as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can, make a few more\Nout of these, and that should cover it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll be happy to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you want to take this with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.44,0:14:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mr. Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.70,0:14:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Please hold on to that young woman\Nwith everything you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She's like a gemstone in the rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Only with care and polish\Ncan those stones ever shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The garments that you're purchasing today,\Nthis is only the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever it takes\Nor you'll lose this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Polish her with your love\Nand abundant wealth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You will have the pleasure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}of dressing a gorgeous young lady\Nto your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I miss you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.43,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,SWEETS SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good? Like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's, um, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Your facial expression tells me\Nyou don't think that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I've seen you smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.15,0:15:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy! It's nothing\Nyou need to be apologizing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.08,0:16:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see what you would be like\Nif you were truly smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kudo, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to respond to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No. You have not upset me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.55,0:16:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no need to cower\Nor say you're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The way things are going,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}marriage is most likely\Nwhat's next for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Being able to say\Nwhat's on our minds is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I would prefer it\Nif you were honest like that
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.28,0:16:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than always apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage is what is next for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He must not know\Nthe truth about me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.55,0:16:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wasn't born with any gifts.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to tell him eventually, but...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.39,0:17:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have this feeling, this strong feeling{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that I should be by his side\Nfor as long as I can.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there's a punishment,\NI'll quietly accept it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.95,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But please let me stay here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let me stay with him...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}until the day I set things right.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just until then...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo is still soaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yurie, I thought that you'd gone home\Nfor the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, my day is never done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.38,0:17:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.76,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This... Lord Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Do with it whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks too valuable. I can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's no reason not to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That gift is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.69,0:18:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you leave it outside my door?\NYou did, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're gifting her a comb,\Nthen that implies a proposal.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't read too deeply into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're proposing then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simply a comb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to gift it, so I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course that's why.\NJust a kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.87,0:19:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Miyo's been using\Na broken comb this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.18,0:19:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So the new one she'll use\Nfor many years to come
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,was just a thoughtful gesture\Nfrom someone who cares for her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.30,0:19:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So wonderfully different\Nfrom all the other women who've come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You have my full support\Nwith her, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.19,0:19:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no doubt\Nthat Miss Miyo will find it to her liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In any case,\Ndon't you hesitate at all to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you very much, Lord Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cherish it for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a pretty typical case
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.83,0:19:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,for those families with abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still a bit unbecoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At any rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,prestigious families shouldn't\Nbe acting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out,\NShinichi Saimori was arranged
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to be married due to some family issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,His wife ended up giving birth\Nto a daughter, Miyo Saimori.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanoko was his lover,\Nand if I have to guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,she's pretty resentful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So they're just vindictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.12,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What else? The real issue?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.41,0:20:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, it's exactly what you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo Saimori doesn't have the gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.88,0:20:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other hand,\Nher half-sister Kaya demonstrated
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit-Sight at the age of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That probably just spurned on anger\Nover the first marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Justifying how they treated Miyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}An abusive stepmother\Nwho hates her...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and no love from her father.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.77,0:20:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She endured all of that alone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.61,0:20:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Giving her a few new kimonos...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.03,0:20:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Some gifts couldn't heal any of this.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These scars are too deep.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, almost forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's this one other thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- Um-hm?\N- It's about Shinichi's first wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're truly not gonna believe it\Nwhen I tell you about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman was a blood relative\Nof the Usuba family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I thought the story was all cock-and-bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.22,0:21:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So far as I was aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}the Usuba family is\Njust about impossible to track down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember right,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.60,0:21:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the Usubas possess a gift that allows them\Nto intervene with a person's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know if that was correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.02,0:21:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Miyo Saimori's actual birthmother is\NSumi Usuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I wasn't able\Nto find out anything on how or why
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}she was married into the Saimoris.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.45,0:21:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Still light out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Since she's arrived here,\NI go home earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Ridiculous! What fool would do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sending shiki-gami\Nto spy on me is child's play.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, who would dare be so bold?
